On the other end of the spectrum, with our reserve of cash if we can make a significant acquisition of a company that would generate real sales and earnings, then that might be subject to the more traditional analysis of what is the maximum we could pay to generate shareholder value. And then that gets into the EBITDA multiples that Eric had mentioned earlier.
