John Wood
- Analogic Corporation  President and CEO
Well as we were saying earlier, I hesitate to give anything approaching guidance but I can tell you with confidence that we've got a multilayer product introduction plan that is going to be bringing some nice stuff out there and we know for instance that we cannot go on spending at this ratio of R&D to sales for a very long time because we would truly test investor patience. So we expect that we're going to be able to grow out of that situation by building sales as these various programs bear fruit.
