(a) The authorized capital stock of Camtronics consists of 100,000 shares of Common Stock, $.01 par value per share, of which 61,599 shares are duly authorized and validly issued and outstanding, fully paid and non-assessable. Seller is the record and beneficial owners of the Shares and has good and valid title to the Shares, free and clear of any Liens and restrictions of any kind. Except for the Shares, there are no shares of capital stock or other equity securities of Camtronics outstanding.
