Refunds and Credits
(i) If Purchaser receives a refund with respect to Taxes arising in a Pre-Closing Tax Period, Purchaser shall pay within 30 days following the receipt of such Tax refund, the amount of such Tax refund to Seller, net of any Tax costs of the receipt of such refund.
