We received today your letter withdrawing the stockholder proposal for Analogic's 2007 annual meeting of stockholders that you previously submitted on behalf of Catalysis Partners, LLC. Please be aware that your proposal would in any event not have been included in the proxy materials for the 2007 annual meeting of stockholders because it was not received until November 14, 2006, which was after the August 21, 2006, deadline specified in Analogic's 2005 Proxy Statement for such proposals.
