and printer following the Company's removal of all confidential and proprietary information. Mr. Millerick agrees to repay to the Company the amounts of any temporary or permanent advances previously made to him by the Company which remain outstanding and any unpaid balances on any credit cards of monies due to the Company or for which the Company is a guarantor.
