(a) . The parties acknowledge that the Hotel employees are employees of Manager (or its affiliates) and not Seller. Hotel Seller warrants that it has no employees. Purchaser shall have full right and authority to meet or communicate with the Manager and, to the extent permitted to do so by Manager, other employees of the Hotel for purposes of understanding and documenting future obligations under the Management Agreement to be assumed by Purchaser, recent and projected financial results for the Hotel and other matters related to Purchaser's pending acquisition of the Hotel. Purchaser shall keep Seller informed of the discussions.
