7.06 Restricted Payments
(a) each Subsidiary may make Restricted Payments to the Borrower, its Subsidiaries and any other Person that owns an Equity Interest in such Subsidiary, ratably according to their respective holdings of the type of Equity Interest in respect of which such Restricted Payment is being made;
