Item 8.01 Other Events.
On November 28, 2011 Analogic Corporation (the "Company") issued a news release announcing a new global branding initiative. The news release incorrectly stated the Company's outlook for revenue growth in fiscal year 2012. Also on November 28, 2011, the Company issued a revised news release that correctly states the Company's outlook for revenue growth. The revised press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1.
