Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition
On March 11, 2013, Analogic Corporation (the "Registrant") announced its financial results for the fiscal quarter and six months ended January 31, 2013. The full text of the press release issued in connection with the announcement is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
